content: http://dogem.onlineINTRODUCTIONDOGEM is startup project with service of online social and communication apk for pupils of Indonesia. With the terms of early service delivery for public the offer might be available only for public of Indonesia. As we dedicated the work to deliver the culture friendly customs of service on following the demographic and daily casuals of pupils of Indonesia.DOGM token Pre Sale will be available during our crowdsale beginning on May 15, 2022 and will last for 90 daysDOGEM Bounty will lasts for 15 weeksWeek 1 start at May 15 and will finish at August 31, 2022  1. Payments will be rolled out weekly.2. Spam/Unpaid posts will not be rolled over for next week either.3. Payment will not be made to those who fail to reach the minimum post quota.4. Payments will be made from escrow address after completion of the ICO terms.5. Negative trust as well as banned members aren't eligible for joining in this campaign. During the campaign period, if you receive a valid negative trust from a other member, or get banned by a moderator, you'll be disqualified immediately from the campaign.6. Users participating with multiple accounts in this campaign, will be kicked out immediately without any payment.7. You must not change the signature while you are participating in the campaign. You'll be monitored frequently by the campaign manager.8. Post in these boards (Off-topic, Local Boards, Archival, Games and rounds) will not be counted for payment.9. Spam, "+1",  flaming, single word (or image), short sentence, writing "bump" only, trolling, “me too”, “thanks”,  smileys only - these posts will not be counted.10. Wearing multiple signatures are not allowed. Anyone wearing multiple signatures will be kicked out from the campaign without payment.11. All valid posts must have an average of 80 characters. (excluding symbols, punctuation and smileys)12. Posts in this threads related to signature campaigns, as well as on any Signature/Avatar/Twitter/Facebook campaigns or on any other contest threads will not be counted.13. Participants should not double post a reply for a particular comment.14. If the rank of a participant gets promoted, he will have to post here as a reminder for updating our spreadsheet.15. A participant will not be paid if he completes 80% of his maximum post quota within 1 day. (i.e. 10 posts within a day)16. Phoscoin reserves the right to make any changes in payment as well as in "Terms and Conditions" of this campaign, at any point of time.BOUNTY ALLOCATIONSignature             25%Article               20%Instagram/Tiktok      25%Video/Youtube         20%Offline campaign      10%CAMPAIGN RATESJr Member and Member: 3 stakes per weekFull Member: 4 stakes per weekSr Member: 6 stakes per weekHero and Legendary: 8 stakes per weekPROOF OF AUTHENTICATIONCode:Proof Of Registration Format (All participants must send 1 time):#PROOF OF REGISTRATIONForum Username:Forum Profile Link:Telegram Username:Participated Campaigns:ETH/BSC Wallet Address:SIGNATURE CAMPAIGN1.
